ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Import Control List
PrecisOrder Amending the IMPORT CONTROL LIST in order to maintain carbon and specialty steel on the Import Control List which aims to provide industry stakeholders with accurate and timely statistics on imports into Canada and to facilitate early detection of the dumping of goods on the Canadian market.
